sections.heading: within village or city; how treated
sections.text: Section 70-305 shall not be construed to grant any rights within the corporate limits of any village or city in this state.SourceLaws 1903, c. 117, § 1, p. 608;R.S.1913, § 7420;Laws 1917, c. 135, § 1, p. 320;Laws 1921, c. 259, § 1, p. 874;C.S.1922, § 7099;C.S.1929
